title: Sidewall, "Diaper", 1863–70

description:
Framework of squares enclosing foliage rinceaux. Alternate squares in alternate rows enclosed radiating petal form of flower. 
Five color combinations: 
a) dark blues on blue ground; b) greens on white; c) neutral blue-green on olive; d) greens on light green; e) reds on red.
